{"tid":493422,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】久違嘅糞Game時間，之後可能會FIFA Pro Club Day156 8/12","createTime":"2017-12-08T13:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T17:51:27.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d846c5f4cac150ced5d907c7782fd6eec83ec1fa","tid":493422,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c103ed39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2B4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7a9887ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"0486857fb9b7800b52ab2144207e82a1878a4ba3","tid":493422,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a618c4c1dfbc9fbed0ee095056c9ab3b0bbc18d7","tid":493422,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37800cc90666fbe4ed982